Welcome to FireFlyOS.

This project aims to develop an operating system to introduce upcoming cybersecurity pro and experienced programmer Sophia 
Pasquarella.

This is meant to grow my skills primarily in the JavaScript scripting language, as I am mostly competent in Python, C++ and markup languages.
It's the first time I've actually made an operating system, so I really want it to turn out well. This will introduce who I am professionally 
and give my portfolio. I also intend to update this with my new cybersecurity findings as I am learning to become an ethical hacker.